#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You are about %(levels)s skill level(s) — roughly %(days)s day(s) of "
"training — from flying %(doctrine)s, which your goal «%(goal)s» targets. "
"Based on your skills as of %(as_of)s."
msgstr ""
"Estás a unos %(levels)s nivel(es) de habilidad —aproximadamente %(days)s "
"día(s) de entrenamiento— de poder volar %(doctrine)s, que es lo que persigue "
"tu objetivo «%(goal)s». Basado en tus habilidades a fecha de %(as_of)s."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You are about %(levels)s skill level(s) — roughly %(days)s day(s) — from "
"flying %(doctrine)s, a corp priority-%(priority)s doctrine. Entirely "
"optional — your call."
msgstr ""
"Estás a unos %(levels)s nivel(es) de habilidad —aproximadamente %(days)s "
"día(s)— de poder volar %(doctrine)s, una doctrine de la corp con prioridad "
"%(priority)s. Totalmente opcional: tú decides."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"«%(operation)s» (%(op_type)s) forms up %(when)s EVE and matches your goal "
"«%(goal)s»."
msgstr ""
"«%(operation)s» (%(op_type)s) se forma %(when)s EVE y encaja con tu objetivo "
"«%(goal)s»."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"«%(operation)s» (%(op_type)s) forms up %(when)s EVE and matches something "
"you enjoy. Optional — your call."
msgstr ""
"«%(operation)s» (%(op_type)s) se forma %(when)s EVE y encaja con algo que "
"disfrutas. Opcional: tú decides."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(count)s mentor(s) currently cover %(category)s, which matches your goal "
"«%(goal)s». Mentors only ever see what you explicitly share."
msgstr ""
"Ahora mismo %(count)s mentor(es) cubren %(category)s, que encaja con tu "
"objetivo «%(goal)s». Los mentores solo ven aquello que compartes "
"explícitamente."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"«%(goal)s» hasn't moved in about %(weeks)s week(s). That's completely fine — "
"interests change. If it helps, you could lower its priority, pause it, or "
"adjust the target date."
msgstr ""
"«%(goal)s» no ha avanzado en unas %(weeks)s semana(s). No pasa absolutamente "
"nada: los intereses cambian. Si te sirve, puedes bajarle la prioridad, "
"pausarlo o ajustar la fecha objetivo."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"«%(goal)s» is blocked: %(blockers)s. You can edit the milestone, pick a "
"different doctrine, or keep the goal parked until this resolves — nothing "
"expires."
msgstr ""
"«%(goal)s» está bloqueado: %(blockers)s. Puedes editar el hito, elegir otra "
"doctrine o dejar el objetivo aparcado hasta que se resuelva; nada caduca."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid "The corp shipyard can supply a %(ship)s for your goal «%(goal)s»."
msgstr ""
"El astillero de la corp puede suministrarte un %(ship)s para tu objetivo "
"«%(goal)s»."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The corp shipyard can supply a %(ship)s for your goal «%(goal)s». It fits "
"within your configured monthly budget."
msgstr ""
"El astillero de la corp puede suministrarte un %(ship)s para tu objetivo "
"«%(goal)s». Entra dentro del presupuesto mensual que has configurado."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Campaign «%(campaign)s» is asking for help: «%(objective)s». This matches "
"your interest in %(activity)s. Volunteering is entirely optional and visible "
"to the campaign team."
msgstr ""
"La campaña «%(campaign)s» pide ayuda: «%(objective)s». Encaja con tu interés "
"en %(activity)s. Ofrecerte es totalmente opcional y visible para el equipo "
"de la campaña."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"It's been a while since you looked at «%(goal)s». A two-minute review keeps "
"the plan honest — reprioritise, adjust the date, or archive it guilt-free."
msgstr ""
"Hace tiempo que no miras «%(goal)s». Una revisión de dos minutos mantiene el "
"plan honesto: cámbiale la prioridad, ajusta la fecha o archívalo sin "
"remordimientos."

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
msgid ""
"It's been a while since you reviewed your preferences. A quick look keeps "
"your suggestions relevant — update what you enjoy, your pace, or your budget "
"any time."
msgstr ""
"Hace tiempo que no revisas tus preferencias. Un vistazo rápido mantiene tus "
"sugerencias relevantes: actualiza lo que disfrutas, tu ritmo o tu "
"presupuesto cuando quieras."

