#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"New to the corp or to EVE? Our veterans will fly with you and show you the "
"ropes — from your first overview setup to your first fleet kill. Sign up as "
"a cadet, get paired with a mentor, and work through hands-on field exercises "
"at your own pace."
msgstr ""
"¿Nuevo en la corp o en EVE? Nuestros veteranos volarán contigo y te "
"enseñarán cómo va todo, desde tu primera configuración del overview hasta tu "
"primer derribo en flota. Apúntate como cadete, te emparejamos con un mentor "
"y avanza por ejercicios prácticos de campo a tu propio ritmo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Welcome to the Corporation"
msgstr "Bienvenido a la Corporación"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "EVE Client & Overview Setup"
msgstr "Configuración del cliente de EVE y del overview"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Travel, Safety & Survival"
msgstr "Viaje, seguridad y supervivencia"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Ship Fitting & Doctrine Basics"
msgstr "Fitting de naves y fundamentos de doctrine"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "PvP Basics"
msgstr "Conceptos básicos de PvP"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Fleet Operations"
msgstr "Operaciones de flota"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Logistics & Buyback Services"
msgstr "Servicios de logística y buyback"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Manufacturing & Industry"
msgstr "Fabricación e industria"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Skill Planning"
msgstr "Planificación de skills"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get plugged into comms, people and the way we do things."
msgstr "Conéctate a las comms, la gente y nuestra forma de hacer las cosas."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Make the client actually readable — overview, brackets, windows."
msgstr ""
"Haz que el cliente sea de verdad legible: overview, brackets y ventanas."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get where you're going and come back alive."
msgstr "Llega a donde vas y vuelve con vida."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Understand slots, tank, and why a doctrine fit is a doctrine fit."
msgstr ""
"Entiende los slots, el tank y por qué un doctrine fit es un doctrine fit."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Make ISK from rats without feeding your ship to a roam."
msgstr "Consigue ISK con las rats sin regalar tu nave a un roam."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Pull ore, compress it, and feed the buyback."
msgstr "Extrae mineral, comprímelo y alimenta el buyback."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Scan it down, hack it, and get out clean."
msgstr "Escanéalo, hackéalo y sal limpio."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Tackle, hold point, follow the FC, and learn from the mail."
msgstr "Haz tackle, mantén el point, sigue al FC y aprende del mail."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Anchor, align, broadcast — be an asset in a fleet."
msgstr "Haz anchor, alinéate, usa el broadcast: sé un activo en la flota."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Move things and turn loot into ISK, the corp way."
msgstr "Mueve cosas y convierte el loot en ISK, a la manera de la corp."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Blueprints, ME/TE, and installing your first job."
msgstr "Blueprints, ME/TE e instalar tu primer job."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Train the right skills in the right order."
msgstr "Entrena las skills correctas en el orden correcto."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Read the corp rules & culture"
msgstr "Lee las reglas y la cultura de la corp"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Set up Discord / Mumble comms"
msgstr "Configura las comms de Discord / Mumble"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn who the officers & FCs are"
msgstr "Aprende quiénes son los oficiales y los FCs"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Understand corp services (SRP, buyback, logistics, doctrines)"
msgstr "Entiende los servicios de la corp (SRP, buyback, logística, doctrines)"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Link your character & grant baseline ESI"
msgstr "Vincula tu personaje y concede el ESI básico"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Have your first onboarding chat with your mentor"
msgstr "Ten tu primera charla de bienvenida con tu mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Configure your overview"
msgstr "Configura tu overview"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Configure brackets & the tactical display"
msgstr "Configura los brackets y la pantalla táctica"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Lay out local, d-scan and the fleet window"
msgstr "Organiza el local, el d-scan y la ventana de flota"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Mentor reviews your UI setup"
msgstr "El mentor revisa tu configuración de UI"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn session-change timers & gate cloak"
msgstr "Aprende los temporizadores de cambio de sesión y el gate cloak"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to use directional scan"
msgstr "Aprende a usar el escaneo direccional"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Create safe spots, tacticals & bookmarks"
msgstr "Crea puntos seguros, tácticos y marcadores"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Complete a travel exercise with your mentor"
msgstr "Completa un ejercicio de viaje con tu mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn high/mid/low/rig/drone/cargo slots"
msgstr "Aprende los slots high/mid/low/rig/drone/cargo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn CPU/PG, cap, resists, tank, range & application"
msgstr "Aprende CPU/PG, cap, resistencias, tank, alcance y aplicación"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review a corp doctrine fit with your mentor"
msgstr "Revisa un doctrine fit de la corp con tu mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Be able to fly a corp doctrine ship"
msgstr "Sé capaz de volar una nave de doctrine de la corp"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Create a skill plan toward a doctrine"
msgstr "Crea un plan de skills orientado a una doctrine"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn safe ratting practice & aligning out"
msgstr "Aprende a hacer ratting de forma segura y a alinearte para salir"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn site selection & when to dock up"
msgstr "Aprende a elegir sites y cuándo atracar"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a ratting session with your mentor nearby"
msgstr "Haz una sesión de ratting con tu mentor cerca"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review a near-miss, loss or good tick"
msgstr "Repasa un casi-desastre, una pérdida o un buen tick"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn mining ship roles & compression"
msgstr "Aprende los roles de las naves de minería y la compresión"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the corp buyback flow"
msgstr "Aprende el flujo del buyback de la corp"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Join a mining session"
msgstr "Únete a una sesión de minería"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Submit a buyback lot"
msgstr "Envía un lote de buyback"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn probe scanning"
msgstr "Aprende el escaneo con sondas"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the hacking minigame"
msgstr "Aprende el minijuego de hackeo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn wormhole safety basics"
msgstr "Aprende los conceptos básicos de seguridad en wormholes"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Complete an exploration practice run"
msgstr "Completa una práctica de exploración"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn tackle: scram, web, point, prop & transversal"
msgstr "Aprende el tackle: scram, web, point, prop y transversal"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to follow FC commands & broadcasts"
msgstr "Aprende a seguir las órdenes del FC y los broadcasts"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Join a training roam or home-defence fleet"
msgstr "Únete a un roam de entrenamiento o a una flota de defensa del hogar"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review a killmail or lossmail with your mentor"
msgstr "Repasa un killmail o lossmail con tu mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn fleet roles, anchoring & the watchlist"
msgstr "Aprende los roles de flota, el anchoring y la lista de seguimiento"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Demonstrate correct broadcast usage"
msgstr "Demuestra un uso correcto del broadcast"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Fly a real corp fleet op"
msgstr "Vuela en una op de flota real de la corp"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Complete a mentor debrief after the op"
msgstr "Haz un debrief con tu mentor después de la op"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn how to request freight & how courier contracts work"
msgstr "Aprende a solicitar freight y cómo funcionan los contratos de courier"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the corp buyback rules"
msgstr "Aprende las reglas del buyback de la corp"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Complete a courier contract (or example)"
msgstr "Completa un contrato de courier (o un ejemplo)"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Mentor confirms you understand the flow"
msgstr "El mentor confirma que entiendes el flujo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn blueprint basics (BPO vs BPC)"
msgstr "Aprende los conceptos básicos de los blueprints (BPO vs BPC)"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn material & time efficiency"
msgstr "Aprende la eficiencia de material y de tiempo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Install a small industry job"
msgstr "Instala un pequeño job de industria"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review cost, materials & output with your mentor"
msgstr "Revisa el coste, los materiales y la producción con tu mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review your current skills with your mentor"
msgstr "Revisa tus skills actuales con tu mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Choose a short-term training goal"
msgstr "Elige un objetivo de entrenamiento a corto plazo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Create a doctrine-relevant skill plan"
msgstr "Crea un plan de skills relevante para una doctrine"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Re-check progress after a couple of weeks"
msgstr "Vuelve a comprobar el progreso al cabo de un par de semanas"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Read the corp rules and code of conduct end to end."
msgstr "Lee las reglas de la corp y el código de conducta de principio a fin."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Install and log into the corp's comms tool and join the right channels."
msgstr ""
"Instala e inicia sesión en la herramienta de comms de la corp y únete a los "
"canales correctos."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn how to recognise officers, directors and fleet commanders."
msgstr "Aprende a reconocer a los oficiales, directores y fleet commanders."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Learn what SRP, buyback, freight and doctrines are and when to use them."
msgstr "Aprende qué son SRP, buyback, freight y doctrines, y cuándo usarlos."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Link your main character so the tools can help you."
msgstr ""
"Vincula tu personaje principal para que las herramientas puedan ayudarte."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Sit down (on comms) with your mentor for a first proper chat."
msgstr ""
"Siéntate (en comms) con tu mentor para una primera charla en condiciones."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Set up a clean overview with the right tabs and columns."
msgstr "Configura un overview limpio con las pestañas y columnas correctas."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Tune brackets so grid is readable at a glance."
msgstr "Ajusta los brackets para que el grid se lea de un vistazo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Dock the local, directional-scan and fleet windows where you can see them."
msgstr ""
"Acopla las ventanas de local, escaneo direccional y flota donde puedas "
"verlas."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Share your screen (or a screenshot) so your mentor can review your UI."
msgstr ""
"Comparte tu pantalla (o una captura) para que tu mentor pueda revisar tu UI."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Understand session timers, gate cloak and the 'don't decloak into a camp' "
"rule."
msgstr ""
"Entiende los temporizadores de sesión, el gate cloak y la regla de 'no "
"descloakear dentro de un camp'."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to read d-scan — angle, range, and what a probe on scan means."
msgstr ""
"Aprende a leer el d-scan: ángulo, alcance y qué significa una sonda en el "
"escaneo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Make a few safes and tactical bookmarks in your home system."
msgstr ""
"Crea unos cuantos puntos seguros y marcadores tácticos en tu sistema base."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Fly a short route with your mentor, using safes and d-scan the whole way."
msgstr ""
"Vuela una ruta corta con tu mentor, usando puntos seguros y el d-scan todo "
"el camino."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn what each slot type is for."
msgstr "Aprende para qué sirve cada tipo de slot."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Understand the core fitting stats and the trade-offs between them."
msgstr "Entiende las stats clave del fitting y los compromisos entre ellas."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Open a corp doctrine fit and go through every module with your mentor."
msgstr "Abre un doctrine fit de la corp y repasa cada módulo con tu mentor."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Train into (or confirm you can already fly) at least one active doctrine "
"ship."
msgstr ""
"Entrena hacia (o confirma que ya puedes volar) al menos una nave de doctrine "
"activa."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Use the skills tool to build a plan toward a doctrine hull."
msgstr ""
"Usa la herramienta de skills para crear un plan orientado a una nave de "
"doctrine."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to rat aligned, watch local/intel, and dock when it's spicy."
msgstr ""
"Aprende a ratear alineado, vigila el local/intel y atraca cuando la cosa se "
"ponga fea."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn which sites to run and the triggers to stop."
msgstr "Aprende qué sites hacer y las señales para parar."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a ratting session while your mentor is on comms / nearby."
msgstr "Haz una sesión de ratting mientras tu mentor está en comms / cerca."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Talk through what happened on a run — good or bad."
msgstr "Comenta qué pasó en una salida, buena o mala."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the mining hull roles and why compression matters."
msgstr ""
"Aprende los roles de las naves de minería y por qué importa la compresión."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn how to turn ore into ISK via corp buyback."
msgstr "Aprende a convertir el mineral en ISK mediante el buyback de la corp."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Join a fleet mine (or mine near your mentor) and pull some ore."
msgstr ""
"Únete a una minería en flota (o mina cerca de tu mentor) y extrae algo de "
"mineral."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Submit a real buyback lot for your ore."
msgstr "Envía un lote real al buyback con tu mineral."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to scan down cosmic signatures with probes."
msgstr "Aprende a escanear cosmic signatures con probes."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Practice the data/relic hacking minigame."
msgstr "Practica el minijuego de hacking de data/relic."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the rules for entering and leaving wormholes safely."
msgstr "Aprende las reglas para entrar y salir de wormholes con seguridad."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Do a supervised exploration run and talk through each site."
msgstr "Haz una salida de exploración supervisada y comenta cada sitio."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn what scram/web/point do and how transversal keeps you alive."
msgstr ""
"Aprende qué hacen scram/web/point y cómo el transversal te mantiene vivo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the standard FC calls and how to use broadcasts."
msgstr "Aprende las llamadas estándar del FC y cómo usar los broadcasts."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get on a killmail with the corp — a roam, gank or home defence."
msgstr ""
"Consigue estar en un killmail con la corp — un roam, gank o defensa de casa."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Pull up a recent kill or loss and talk through what happened."
msgstr "Abre un kill o una pérdida reciente y comenta qué pasó."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn wings/squads, anchoring, and what the watchlist is for."
msgstr "Aprende wings/squads, el anchoring y para qué sirve la watchlist."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Show you can broadcast for reps/target/align correctly."
msgstr ""
"Demuestra que puedes hacer broadcast de reps/target/align correctamente."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Sign up for and fly a corp operation."
msgstr "Apúntate y vuela en una operación de la corp."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Debrief the op with your mentor afterwards."
msgstr "Haz el debrief de la op con tu mentor después."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to book a courier and what collateral/reward mean."
msgstr "Aprende a contratar un courier y qué significan collateral/reward."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn what buyback pays and where."
msgstr "Aprende cuánto paga el buyback y dónde."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a real courier contract through the freight service."
msgstr "Ejecuta un contrato courier real a través del servicio de freight."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Talk your mentor through the whole logistics flow."
msgstr "Explícale a tu mentor todo el flujo de logística."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the difference between BPOs and BPCs."
msgstr "Aprende la diferencia entre BPOs y BPCs."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn what ME/TE do and why they matter."
msgstr "Aprende qué hacen ME/TE y por qué importan."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Install a small manufacturing or research job."
msgstr "Instala un pequeño trabajo de fabricación o investigación."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Go over the BOM and margin of your job with your mentor."
msgstr "Repasa el BOM y el margen de tu trabajo con tu mentor."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Go through your current skills and gaps with your mentor."
msgstr "Repasa tus skills actuales y sus carencias con tu mentor."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Pick a concrete short-term skill goal."
msgstr "Elige un objetivo de skill concreto a corto plazo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Build a skill plan toward a corp doctrine."
msgstr "Crea un plan de skills hacia una doctrine de la corp."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Come back to your mentor after ~2 weeks to review progress."
msgstr "Vuelve con tu mentor tras ~2 semanas para revisar el progreso."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Point your cadet at the rules doc; answer any questions."
msgstr ""
"Dirige a tu cadete al documento de reglas; responde cualquier pregunta."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm your cadet can hear and be heard on comms."
msgstr "Confirma que tu cadete puede oír y ser oído en comms."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Walk through the org chart and who to ask for what."
msgstr "Repasa el organigrama y a quién pedir cada cosa."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Give the tour of the corp's services and expectations."
msgstr "Haz el recorrido por los servicios y expectativas de la corp."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the cadet's character is linked and skills import."
msgstr ""
"Confirma que el personaje del cadete está vinculado y que las skills se "
"importan."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Have a relaxed first session — goals, timezones, what they want from EVE."
msgstr ""
"Ten una primera sesión relajada — objetivos, zonas horarias, qué quieren de "
"EVE."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review the cadet's overview live; fix obvious gaps."
msgstr ""
"Revisa el overview del cadete en directo; corrige las carencias obvias."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Sanity-check bracket settings."
msgstr "Verifica la configuración de brackets."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the window layout works."
msgstr "Confirma que la distribución de ventanas funciona."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Do a full pass over the cadet's UI and overview."
msgstr "Haz una revisión completa de la UI y el overview del cadete."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain session timers and cloak with real examples."
msgstr "Explica los session timers y el cloak con ejemplos reales."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a live d-scan drill with your cadet."
msgstr "Haz un ejercicio de d-scan en directo con tu cadete."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Verify the cadet's safes are actually safe (off-grid)."
msgstr "Verifica que los safes del cadete son realmente seguros (off-grid)."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Take the cadet on a supervised travel run through a chokepoint."
msgstr ""
"Lleva al cadete en un viaje supervisado a través de un cuello de botella."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Walk through slot layout on a real hull."
msgstr "Repasa la distribución de slots en un hull real."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain the fitting stats with a doctrine fit open."
msgstr "Explica las stats del fitting con un doctrine fit abierto."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain why each module is on the doctrine fit."
msgstr "Explica por qué cada module está en el doctrine fit."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Help the cadet pick the fastest doctrine to get into."
msgstr "Ayuda al cadete a elegir la doctrine más rápida en la que entrar."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Help pick a sensible first doctrine skill goal."
msgstr "Ayuda a elegir un primer objetivo de skill de doctrine sensato."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain ratting safety and the 'align out' habit."
msgstr "Explica la seguridad al hacer ratting y el hábito de 'align out'."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Cover site choice and bail triggers."
msgstr "Cubre la elección de sitios y las señales para huir."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Watch intel and coach while your cadet rats."
msgstr "Vigila el intel y orienta mientras tu cadete hace ratting."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Debrief a real ratting moment with your cadet."
msgstr "Haz el debrief de un momento real de ratting con tu cadete."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain mining ships, boosts and compression."
msgstr "Explica las naves de minería, los boosts y la compresión."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Walk through submitting a buyback lot."
msgstr "Repasa cómo enviar un lote de buyback."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get the cadet into a mining op and confirm they mined."
msgstr "Mete al cadete en una op de minería y confirma que minó."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the cadet submitted a buyback lot."
msgstr "Confirma que el cadete envió un lote de buyback."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a scanning drill with your cadet."
msgstr "Haz un ejercicio de escaneo con tu cadete."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Share hacking tips (node types, virus strength)."
msgstr "Comparte consejos de hacking (tipos de nodos, potencia del virus)."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Cover WH mass/time and the 'bookmark both sides' rule."
msgstr "Cubre la masa/tiempo de los WH y la regla de 'marcar ambos lados'."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Take the cadet on a low-risk exploration run."
msgstr "Lleva al cadete en una salida de exploración de bajo riesgo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain tackle and range control with examples."
msgstr "Explica el tackle y el control de rango con ejemplos."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a quick comms/broadcast drill."
msgstr "Haz un ejercicio rápido de comms/broadcast."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Bring your cadet on a low-stakes fleet and get them on a mail."
msgstr ""
"Lleva a tu cadete en una flota de bajo riesgo y consíguele estar en un mail."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Debrief a real mail — what went right, what to change."
msgstr "Haz el debrief de un mail real — qué salió bien, qué cambiar."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain fleet structure and anchoring."
msgstr "Explica la estructura de la flota y el anchoring."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Check the cadet broadcasts the right things at the right time."
msgstr ""
"Comprueba que el cadete hace broadcast de las cosas correctas en el momento "
"correcto."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get your cadet on a scheduled op and keep an eye on them."
msgstr "Mete a tu cadete en una op programada y vigílalo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a short after-action with your cadet."
msgstr "Haz un breve after-action con tu cadete."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Walk through booking a freight contract."
msgstr "Repasa cómo reservar un contrato de freight."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain the buyback rates and locations."
msgstr "Explica las tarifas y ubicaciones del buyback."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the cadet completed (and ideally ESI-verified) a haul."
msgstr ""
"Confirma que el cadete completó (e idealmente verificó por ESI) un haul."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the cadet understands collateral, reward and risk."
msgstr "Confirma que el cadete entiende collateral, reward y el riesgo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain blueprints and runs."
msgstr "Explica los blueprints y las runs."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Show ME/TE impact on a real build."
msgstr "Muestra el impacto de ME/TE en una fabricación real."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Help the cadet install their first job."
msgstr "Ayuda al cadete a instalar su primer trabajo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review the economics of the cadet's job."
msgstr "Revisa la economía del trabajo del cadete."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review the cadet's skills and obvious priorities."
msgstr "Revisa las skills del cadete y las prioridades obvias."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Help pick a motivating first goal."
msgstr "Ayuda a elegir un primer objetivo motivador."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the plan targets a doctrine the corp needs."
msgstr "Confirma que el plan apunta a una doctrine que la corp necesita."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Follow up on the cadet's training progress."
msgstr "Haz seguimiento del progreso de entrenamiento del cadete."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "First Steps"
msgstr "Primeros Pasos"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
