msgstr "Salto Black Ops vía %(cyno)s — tramos covert, menos jump fatigue."

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid "Direct jump-drive route via %(cyno)s."
msgstr "Ruta directa por jump drive vía %(cyno)s."

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't enter high-sec (no stargate access and no cyno in high-"
"sec), so neither the high-sec origin nor the high-sec destination can be "
"reached. Choose a low-sec or null-sec system."
msgstr ""
"Un %(ship)s no puede entrar en high-sec (sin acceso por stargate y sin cyno "
"en high-sec), así que no se puede alcanzar ni el origen high-sec ni el "
"destino high-sec. Elige un sistema low-sec o null-sec."

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't enter high-sec (no stargate access and no cyno in high-"
"sec), so the high-sec destination can't be reached. Choose a low-sec or null-"
"sec system."
msgstr ""
"Un %(ship)s no puede entrar en high-sec (sin acceso por stargate y sin cyno "
"en high-sec), así que no se puede alcanzar el destino high-sec. Elige un "
"sistema low-sec o null-sec."

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't enter high-sec (no stargate access and no cyno in high-"
"sec), so the high-sec origin can't be reached. Choose a low-sec or null-sec "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Un %(ship)s no puede entrar en high-sec (sin acceso por stargate y sin cyno "
"en high-sec), así que no se puede alcanzar el origen high-sec. Elige un "
"sistema low-sec o null-sec."

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't cyno into or out of high-sec: gate out of the high-sec "
"origin to a low-sec entry, jump, then gate to the high-sec destination."
msgstr ""
"Un %(ship)s no puede hacer cyno hacia ni desde high-sec: sal por gate del "
"origen high-sec a una entrada low-sec, salta, y luego llega por gate al "
"destino high-sec."

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't cyno directly into high-sec: jump to a low-sec exit near "
"the destination, then take stargates the rest of the way."
msgstr ""
"Un %(ship)s no puede hacer cyno directamente a high-sec: salta a una salida "
"low-sec cerca del destino y haz el resto del camino por stargates."

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't light a cyno in high-sec: gate out of the high-sec origin "
"to a low-sec staging system, then jump from there."
msgstr ""
"Un %(ship)s no puede encender un cyno en high-sec: sal por gate del origen "
"high-sec a un sistema de staging low-sec y salta desde allí."

#: apps/navigation/views.py
msgid "Grant it on the ESI Scopes page."
msgstr "Concédelo en la página de ESI Scopes."

#: apps/navigation/views.py
