#: apps/onboarding/views.py
msgid ""
"Link your characters and plug into corp comms — this is how we find you and "
"how the Grid briefs you."
msgstr ""
"Vincula tus personajes y conéctate a las comms de la corp — así es como te "
"encontramos y como el Grid te informa."

#: apps/onboarding/views.py
msgid "Show us your skills"
msgstr "Muéstranos tus habilidades"

#: apps/onboarding/views.py
msgid ""
"Share your skill sheet so every tool here can answer 'can I fly this?' "
"honestly."
msgstr ""
"Comparte tu hoja de habilidades para que cada herramienta aquí pueda "
"responder honestamente '¿puedo volar esto?'."

#: apps/onboarding/views.py
msgid "Get combat-ready"
msgstr "Prepárate para el combate"

#: apps/onboarding/views.py
msgid ""
"Train into a corp doctrine ship. Flying what the FC calls for is the single "
"biggest thing you can do."
msgstr ""
"Entrena para una nave doctrine de la corp. Volar lo que pide el FC es lo más "
"importante que puedes hacer."

#: apps/onboarding/views.py
msgid "Live here"
msgstr "Vive aquí"

#: apps/onboarding/views.py
msgid ""
"Move in, undock with us, and start earning — nullsec pays the pilots who "
"show up."
msgstr ""
"Múdate aquí, sal de estación con nosotros y empieza a ganar — nullsec paga a "
"los pilotos que se presentan."

