#: apps/pingboard/notifications.py
msgid ""
"High-severity officer recommendations — stock shortages, doctrine readiness "
"gaps, build-vs-buy calls, market seeding, hauling backlog and repeated "
"combat losses (e.g. “Lost 6 × Capsule in the last 7d”)."
msgstr ""
"Recomendaciones de oficiales de alta severidad — escasez de stock, carencias "
"de preparación de doctrine, decisiones de construir vs. comprar, siembra de "
"mercado, acumulación de transportes pendientes y pérdidas de combate "
"repetidas (p. ej. “Se perdieron 6 × Capsule en los últimos 7 d”)."

#: apps/pingboard/notifications.py
msgid "Beat recommendations.run (every 30 min) → dispatch_alerts."
msgstr "Beat recommendations.run (cada 30 min) → dispatch_alerts."

