msgstr "Canal eliminado."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
msgid "No product selected for this planet."
msgstr "No hay ningún producto seleccionado para este planeta."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
#, python-format
msgid "No market price for %(product)s — revenue shown as 0."
msgstr ""
"Sin precio de mercado para %(product)s — los ingresos se muestran como 0."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
#, python-format
msgid "No price for input %(input)s."
msgstr "Sin precio para el insumo %(input)s."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
msgid "Add at least one planet to estimate profit."
msgstr "Añade al menos un planeta para estimar el beneficio."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
msgid ""
"Some products or inputs are unpriced — profit is understated. Refresh "
"prices, or the daily market sync will fill them in."
msgstr ""
"Algunos productos o insumos no tienen precio — el beneficio está "
"subestimado. Actualiza los precios, o la sincronización diaria de mercado "
"los completará."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
msgid "This setup is currently unprofitable at these prices and taxes."
msgstr ""
"Esta configuración no es rentable actualmente con estos precios e impuestos."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"High tax load (%(pct)s%% before hauling) — check your customs standings and "
"whether hauling to a cheaper hub helps."
msgstr ""
"Carga fiscal alta (%(pct)s%% antes del transporte) — revisa tus standings de "
"aduanas y si transportar a un hub más barato ayuda."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Prices from %(region)s; customs %(export)s%% export / %(import)s%% import; "
"sales %(sales)s%% + broker %(broker)s%%."
msgstr ""
"Precios de %(region)s; aduanas %(export)s%% exportación / %(import)s%% "
"importación; ventas %(sales)s%% + broker %(broker)s%%."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Extraction planets assume a steady %(rate)s/hour per planet — tune this or "
"enter your real output for accuracy."
msgstr ""
"Los planetas de extracción asumen un ritmo constante de %(rate)s/hora por "
"planeta — ajústalo o introduce tu producción real para mayor precisión."

#: apps/planetary/calc.py
msgid ""
"Factory output uses a per-tier planning estimate; enter your measured units/"
"day on each factory planet to refine it."
msgstr ""
"La producción de fábrica usa una estimación de planificación por nivel; "
"introduce tus unidades/día medidas en cada planeta de fábrica para refinarla."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Raw resource"
msgstr "Recurso bruto"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Pulled straight from a planet by an Extractor Control Unit."
msgstr "Extraído directamente de un planeta por una Extractor Control Unit."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"The 15 raw materials. You never sell these — you refine them on-planet into "
"P1. Extraction rate depends on your ECU program and the planet's resource "
"hotspots, so it's the one number you should tune to your colony."
msgstr ""
"Las 15 materias primas. Nunca se venden: se refinan en el propio planeta "
"hasta P1. La tasa de extracción depende de tu programa de ECU y de los "
"puntos calientes de recursos del planeta, así que es la cifra que debes "
"ajustar a tu colonia."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Extractor Control Unit (ECU) + extractor heads"
msgstr "Extractor Control Unit (ECU) + cabezales extractores"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Processed material"
msgstr "Material procesado"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "One P0 refined in a Basic Industry Facility."
msgstr "Un P0 refinado en una Basic Industry Facility."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"15 processed materials. A Basic Industry Facility turns 3,000 of one P0 into "
"20 P1 every 30 minutes. P1 is the first thing worth selling, and the "
"feedstock for everything above it."
msgstr ""
"15 materiales procesados. Una Basic Industry Facility convierte 3.000 "
"unidades de un P0 en 20 P1 cada 30 minutos. El P1 es lo primero que vale la "
"pena vender, y la materia prima de todo lo que está por encima."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Basic Industry Facility (BIF)"
msgstr "Basic Industry Facility (BIF)"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Refined commodity"
msgstr "Producto refinado"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Two P1 combined in an Advanced Industry Facility."
msgstr "Dos P1 combinados en una Advanced Industry Facility."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"Refined commodities combine two P1 inputs. These are the bread-and-butter of "
"profitable PI — good ISK/m³ and steady demand (Coolant, Mechanical Parts, "
"Consumer Electronics, Enriched Uranium…)."
msgstr ""
"Los productos refinados combinan dos insumos P1. Son el pan de cada día del "
"PI rentable: buen ISK/m³ y demanda estable (Coolant, Mechanical Parts, "
"Consumer Electronics, Enriched Uranium…)."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Advanced Industry Facility (AIF)"
msgstr "Advanced Industry Facility (AIF)"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Specialised commodity"
msgstr "Producto especializado"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Several P2 combined into a high-value good."
msgstr "Varios P2 combinados en un bien de alto valor."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"Specialised commodities (Robotics, Coolant→…, Guidance Systems, Transcranial "
"Microcontrollers…). High value per unit but they need a multi-planet supply "
"chain or a market to buy the P2 inputs."
msgstr ""
"Productos especializados (Robotics, Coolant→…, Guidance Systems, "
"Transcranial Microcontrollers…). Alto valor por unidad, pero necesitan una "
"cadena de suministro de varios planetas o un mercado donde comprar los "
"insumos P2."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Advanced commodity"
msgstr "Producto avanzado"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "The end of the chain — mixes P3 (and some P1) into strategic goods."
msgstr ""
"El final de la cadena: mezcla P3 (y algo de P1) para obtener bienes "
"estratégicos."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"Advanced commodities (Nano-Factory, Broadcast Node, Self-Harmonising Power "
"Core, Wetware Mainframe) feed sovereignty structures and capital "
"construction. Only worth it with a dedicated multi-character operation."
msgstr ""
"Los productos avanzados (Nano-Factory, Broadcast Node, Self-Harmonising "
"Power Core, Wetware Mainframe) alimentan las estructuras de soberanía y la "
"construcción de naves capital. Solo compensan con una operación dedicada de "
"varios personajes."

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "High-Tech Production Plant"
msgstr "High-Tech Production Plant"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Which of your pilots will run this colony network. Used to label the plan "
"and to match imported colonies — nothing is changed in-game."
msgstr ""
"Cuál de tus pilotos gestionará esta red de colonias. Se usa para etiquetar "
"el plan y para emparejar colonias importadas — no se cambia nada en el juego."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Pricing hub"
msgstr "Hub de precios"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Where you'll sell. Prices and profit are estimated against this hub. Jita is "
"the most liquid and the safest default."
msgstr ""
"Dónde venderás. Los precios y el beneficio se estiman con respecto a este "
"hub. Jita es el más líquido y la opción por defecto más segura."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "e.g. Jita P2 Coolant run"
msgstr "p. ej. producción de Coolant P2 para Jita"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "e.g. Amamake (optional)"
msgstr "p. ej. Amamake (opcional)"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Anything you want to remember about this setup."
msgstr "Cualquier cosa que quieras recordar sobre esta configuración."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "A short name you'll recognise in your plan list."
msgstr "Un nombre corto que reconocerás en tu lista de planes."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"What you want out of PI. This tunes the recommendations and the guidance."
msgstr ""
"Lo que quieres obtener de PI. Esto ajusta las recomendaciones y la guía."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "The system (or staging) you'll run this from. Optional, for your notes."
msgstr ""
"El sistema (o staging) desde el que lo gestionarás. Opcional, para tus notas."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"How many planets you'll dedicate (1–6). Alpha clones are limited; Omega "
"pilots can run more with the right skills."
msgstr ""
"Cuántos planetas dedicarás (1–6). Los clones Alpha están limitados; los "
"pilotos Omega pueden gestionar más con las habilidades adecuadas."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Where you'll set up. Nullsec/wormhole planets yield more but cost you "
"hauling and danger — this is context for the guidance, not a hard rule."
msgstr ""
"Dónde te establecerás. Los planetas de nullsec/wormhole rinden más pero te "
"cuestan transporte y peligro — esto es contexto para la guía, no una regla "
"estricta."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Customs office (POCO) tax on export, as a %. In hostile space this can be "
"high — check the POCO before you commit."
msgstr ""
"Impuesto de exportación de la aduana (POCO), en %. En espacio hostil puede "
"ser alto — revisa el POCO antes de comprometerte."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "POCO tax on importing materials to a factory planet, as a %."
msgstr ""
"Impuesto del POCO al importar materiales a un planeta de fábrica, en %."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Market sales tax when you sell (%). Scales down with Accounting."
msgstr ""
"Impuesto de venta del mercado al vender (%). Se reduce con la skill "
"Accounting."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Broker fee on sell orders (%). 0 if you only sell to buy orders."
msgstr ""
"Comisión de corretaje en órdenes de venta (%). 0 si solo vendes a órdenes de "
"compra."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"ISK per m³ to move goods to the hub. 0 if you haul yourself. Applied only "
"when the export strategy is 'haul to hub'."
msgstr ""
"ISK por m³ para mover mercancías al hub. 0 si transportas tú mismo. Se "
"aplica solo cuando la estrategia de exportación es 'transportar al hub'."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "If you use corp buyback, the percent of Jita sell it pays."
msgstr ""
"Si usas el buyback de la corp, el % del precio de venta de Jita que paga."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Planning assumption: P0 units/hour on one extraction planet. Tune it to your "
"real colonies for accuracy."
msgstr ""
"Suposición de planificación: unidades de P0/hora en un planeta de "
"extracción. Ajústalo a tus colonias reales para mayor precisión."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"How often you'll reset extractors and haul. Low effort favours simple, long-"
"cycle setups."
msgstr ""
"Con qué frecuencia reiniciarás los extractores y transportarás. El bajo "
"esfuerzo favorece configuraciones simples y de ciclo largo."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "What you'll do with the output — it changes which fees apply."
msgstr "Qué harás con la producción — cambia qué comisiones se aplican."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Who can see this plan. Private is only you."
msgstr "Quién puede ver este plan. Privado eres solo tú."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "— select a pilot —"
msgstr "— selecciona un piloto —"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Enter a percentage between 0 and 100."
msgstr "Introduce un porcentaje entre 0 y 100."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "A pilot can run between 1 and 6 planets."
msgstr "Un piloto puede gestionar entre 1 y 6 planetas."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Default pricing hub"
msgstr "Hub de precios por defecto"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py templates/admin_audit/console/planetary/hub.html
msgid "Corp priority products"
msgstr "Productos prioritarios de la corp"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Comma-separated PI product names the corp wants pilots to make (e.g. "
"Coolant, Mechanical Parts, Robotics). They get a badge in the "
"recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Nombres de productos de PI separados por comas que la corp quiere que los "
"pilotos fabriquen (p. ej. Coolant, Mechanical Parts, Robotics). Reciben una "
"insignia en las recomendaciones."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "e.g. lowsec staging, home constellation"
msgstr "p. ej. staging en lowsec, constelación de origen"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Master switch. Off hides the whole planner from pilots."
msgstr ""
"Interruptor principal. Desactivado oculta todo el planificador a los pilotos."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "A label for this config (only you see it)."
msgstr "Una etiqueta para esta configuración (solo tú la ves)."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Starting extraction assumption for new plans."
msgstr "Suposición de extracción inicial para los nuevos planes."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Percent of Jita sell the corp buyback pays, for plans that use it."
msgstr ""
"% del precio de venta de Jita que paga el buyback de la corp, para los "
"planes que lo usan."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Free text: where the corp suggests running PI."
msgstr "Texto libre: dónde sugiere la corp gestionar PI."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "A short note shown to pilots about what the corp needs."
msgstr "Una nota breve mostrada a los pilotos sobre lo que la corp necesita."

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Default sharing for newly-created plans."
msgstr "Compartición por defecto para los planes recién creados."

#: apps/planetary/issues_i18n.py
msgid "An extractor program has expired — restart it to keep pulling P0."
msgstr ""
"Un programa de extractor ha caducado — reinícialo para seguir extrayendo P0."

#: apps/planetary/issues_i18n.py
msgid "A factory has no schematic set — it isn't producing anything."
msgstr ""
"Una fábrica no tiene ningún schematic asignado — no está produciendo nada."

#: apps/planetary/issues_i18n.py
msgid "No routes configured — nothing will flow between facilities."
msgstr "No hay rutas configuradas — nada fluirá entre las instalaciones."

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "P0 · Raw resource"
msgstr "P0 · Recurso bruto"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "P1 · Processed material"
msgstr "P1 · Material procesado"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "P2 · Refined commodity"
msgstr "P2 · Producto refinado"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "P3 · Specialised commodity"
msgstr "P3 · Producto especializado"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "P4 · Advanced commodity"
msgstr "P4 · Producto avanzado"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "m³ per unit — used for hauling sizing."
msgstr "m³ por unidad — usado para dimensionar el transporte."

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid ""
"Master switch shown to pilots. Turning this off hides the planner even if "
"the feature flag is on."
msgstr ""
"Interruptor principal mostrado a los pilotos. Al desactivarlo se oculta el "
"planificador aunque la función esté habilitada."

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Customs office (POCO) export tax %, applied to item base value."
msgstr ""
"Impuesto de exportación de la aduana (POCO) en %, aplicado al valor base del "
"ítem."

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Market sales tax %."
msgstr "Impuesto de venta del mercado en %."

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "ISK per m³ to move goods to the hub (0 = you self-haul)."
msgstr "ISK por m³ para llevar mercancías al hub (0 = transportas tú mismo)."

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Percent of Jita sell the corp buyback pays."
msgstr "% de la venta en Jita que paga el buyback de la corp."

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Planning assumption: P0 units/hour on one extraction planet."
msgstr ""
"Supuesto de planificación: unidades P0/hora en un planeta de extracción."

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Type ids the corp wants pilots to produce."
msgstr "Los type ids que la corp quiere que los pilotos produzcan."

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Beginner passive income"
msgstr "Ingreso pasivo para principiantes"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Low-effort extraction"
msgstr "Extracción de bajo esfuerzo"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "P0 → P1 processing"
msgstr "Procesamiento P0 → P1"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "P0 → P2 refined"
msgstr "Refinado P0 → P2"

#: apps/planetary/models.py apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Factory planet"
msgstr "Planeta fábrica"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "P3 / P4 advanced production"
msgstr "Producción avanzada P3 / P4"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Corporation supply chain"
msgstr "Cadena de suministro de la corporación"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Maximum ISK profit"
msgstr "Máximo beneficio en ISK"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Ready to build"
msgstr "Listo para construir"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Needs review"
msgstr "Necesita revisión"

#: apps/planetary/models.py
msgid "Shared with corporation"
msgstr "Compartido con la corporación"

