#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid ""
"When armed, the system opens Courses of Action <span class=\"text-cyan\">as "
"proposals</span>, on a schedule, for action families whose track record it "
"trusts. It <span class=\"text-gold\">never</span> accepts a COA, creates a "
"task, or spends ISK — a human still commits every proposal, and every "
"proposal is audited and dismissible. Ships <span class=\"text-gold\">off</"
"span>."
msgstr ""
"Cuando está armado, el sistema abre Cursos de Acción <span class=\"text-"
"cyan\">como propuestas</span>, de forma programada, para las familias de "
"acciones cuyo historial considera fiable. <span class=\"text-gold\">Nunca</"
"span> acepta un COA, crea una tarea ni gasta ISK: un humano sigue "
"confirmando cada propuesta, y toda propuesta queda auditada y se puede "
"descartar. Se entrega <span class=\"text-gold\">desactivado</span>."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "Armed — the daily beat will propose for calibration-trusted families."
msgstr ""
"Armado — el beat diario propondrá para las familias fiables por calibración."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid ""
"Disarmed — the beat fires but proposes nothing (the kill switch is off)."
msgstr ""
"Desarmado — el beat se ejecuta pero no propone nada (el interruptor de corte "
"está apagado)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "Arm autonomous proposal"
msgstr "Armar la propuesta autónoma"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid ""
"The kill switch. Off ⇒ the task returns \"disabled\" and creates nothing."
msgstr ""
"El interruptor de corte. Apagado ⇒ la tarea devuelve \"disabled\" y no crea "
"nada."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "Min calibration samples"
msgstr "Muestras de calibración mín."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid ""
"A family needs at least this many measured outcomes before it can be auto-"
"proposed."
msgstr ""
"Una familia necesita al menos este número de resultados medidos antes de "
"poder proponerse de forma autónoma."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "Max calibration spread"
msgstr "Dispersión de calibración máx."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid ""
"And its prediction-error spread must be at or below this (tighter = more "
"trusted)."
msgstr ""
"Y su dispersión de error de predicción debe ser igual o inferior a este "
"valor (más estrecha = más fiable)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "Max proposals per run"
msgstr "Máx. propuestas por ejecución"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "A hard cap on how many COAs one autonomous run may open."
msgstr "Límite máximo de COA que puede abrir una única ejecución autónoma."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/dimensions.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/finance.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/kpis.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/srp.html
#, python-format
msgid "config v%(version)s"
msgstr "config v%(version)s"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
#, python-format
msgid "last by %(by)s"
msgstr "última por %(by)s"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "Calibration — what would be proposed for now"
msgstr "Calibración — qué se propondría ahora mismo"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid ""
"No measured outcomes yet — nothing is trusted, so autonomous proposal stays "
"silent even when armed. Trust accrues as accepted COAs complete and their "
"outcomes are measured."
msgstr ""
"Aún no hay resultados medidos — nada es fiable, así que la propuesta "
"autónoma permanece en silencio incluso cuando está armada. La confianza se "
"acumula a medida que los COA aceptados se completan y se miden sus "
"resultados."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
#, python-format
msgid "spread %(spread)s"
msgstr "dispersión %(spread)s"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "▲ trusted"
msgstr "▲ fiable"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "○ not yet"
msgstr "○ todavía no"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Classification"
msgstr "Clasificación"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid ""
"Set the default report classification and the tier → minimum-role map that "
"gates who can read each tier. A <span class=\"text-cyan\">design floor</"
"span> is enforced server-side — a tier can be tightened but never loosened "
"below its built-in minimum."
msgstr ""
"Define la clasificación por defecto de los informes y el mapa nivel → rol "
"mínimo que controla quién puede leer cada nivel. El servidor impone un <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">mínimo de diseño</span> — un nivel se puede endurecer, "
"pero nunca relajar por debajo de su mínimo integrado."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid "Default classification"
msgstr "Clasificación por defecto"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid "The tier a report falls back to when its template specifies none."
msgstr ""
"El nivel que se aplica a un informe cuando su plantilla no especifica "
"ninguno."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid "Tier → minimum role"
msgstr "Nivel → rol mínimo"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid ""
"Restores the default classification and every tier floor to the shipped "
"defaults."
msgstr ""
"Restablece la clasificación por defecto y el mínimo de cada nivel a los "
"valores predeterminados de fábrica."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Constraints &amp; thresholds"
msgstr "Restricciones &amp; umbrales"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid ""
"Tune the global severity ratios, demand baselines and which constraint "
"providers run. A threshold change re-colours severities on the <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">next snapshot</span> with no deploy. A net-new provider "
"stays disabled until you enable it here."
msgstr ""
"Ajusta los ratios globales de gravedad, las líneas base de demanda y qué "
"proveedores de restricciones se ejecutan. Un cambio de umbral recolorea las "
"gravedades en la <span class=\"text-cyan\">siguiente instantánea</span>, sin "
"necesidad de despliegue. Un proveedor nuevo permanece desactivado hasta que "
"lo actives aquí."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "Global severity ratios"
msgstr "Ratios globales de gravedad"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "Constraint providers"
msgstr "Proveedores de restricciones"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "No constraint providers are registered."
msgstr "No hay proveedores de restricciones registrados."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "Demand targets"
msgstr "Objetivos de demanda"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid ""
"One per line as <code class=\"text-faint\">key value</code> — e.g. <code "
"class=\"text-faint\">doctrine:ferox-fleet 22</code>. Leave empty to seed "
"demand from data."
msgstr ""
"Uno por línea con el formato <code class=\"text-faint\">clave valor</code> — "
"p. ej. <code class=\"text-faint\">doctrine:ferox-fleet 22</code>. Déjalo "
"vacío para inicializar la demanda a partir de los datos."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid ""
"Restores every ratio, provider flag and demand target to the shipped "
"defaults."
msgstr ""
"Restablece todos los ratios, indicadores de proveedor y objetivos de demanda "
"a los valores predeterminados de fábrica."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Command Intelligence · Scheduled reports &amp; delivery · [FORCA] Command "
"Grid"
msgstr ""
"Inteligencia de mando · Informes programados y entrega · [FORCA] Command Grid"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Scheduled reports &amp; delivery"
msgstr "Informes programados &amp; entrega"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"The weekly briefing generates in the background; delivery is <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">classification-aware</span> and ships <span class=\"text-"
"gold\">disarmed</span> — a director-eyes-only report can never be broadcast "
"to a corp-wide Discord channel (the server refuses that pairing). Nothing "
"leaves the server until you arm a channel and configure its target below."
msgstr ""
"El informe semanal se genera en segundo plano; la entrega <span class=\"text-"
"cyan\">tiene en cuenta la clasificación</span> y se entrega <span "
"class=\"text-gold\">desarmada</span> — un informe de solo para los ojos del "
"director nunca puede difundirse a un canal de Discord de toda la corp (el "
"servidor rechaza esa combinación). Nada sale del servidor hasta que armes un "
"canal y configures su destino más abajo."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"LLM enabled — scheduled briefings are narrated. (Without a key they still "
"generate a deterministic report.)"
msgstr ""
"LLM activado — los informes programados se narran. (Sin una clave se sigue "
"generando un informe determinista.)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"LLM disabled — scheduled briefings still generate the deterministic "
"constraint picture."
msgstr ""
"LLM desactivado — los informes programados siguen generando el cuadro "
"determinista de restricciones."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Scheduled generation"
msgstr "Generación programada"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Generate a weekly briefing"
msgstr "Generar un informe semanal"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Monday 12:00 UTC. Deduped against a recent run so a retried beat never "
"double-spends tokens."
msgstr ""
"Lunes 12:00 UTC. Se deduplica contra una ejecución reciente para que un beat "
"reintentado nunca gaste tokens dos veces."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Only announce when binding at/above"
msgstr "Anunciar solo cuando la restricción vinculante sea igual o superior a"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Suppress delivery of a quiet report with no meaningful constraint."
msgstr "Suprime la entrega de un informe sin restricciones relevantes."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Discord (broadcast)"
msgstr "Discord (difusión)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Arm Discord delivery"
msgstr "Armar la entrega por Discord"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Posts a classification-safe summary to every active Discord webhook "
"(configured under In-game Alerts)."
msgstr ""
"Publica un resumen acorde a la clasificación en cada webhook de Discord "
"activo (configurado en Alertas en el juego)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Broadcast these classifications"
msgstr "Difundir estas clasificaciones"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Only corp-shareable tiers can be broadcast; director/alliance tiers are "
"never offered here."
msgstr ""
"Solo se pueden difundir los niveles compartibles con la corp; los niveles de "
"director/alianza nunca se ofrecen aquí."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "EVE-mail (targeted to leadership)"
msgstr "EVE-mail (dirigido a la dirección)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Arm EVE-mail delivery"
msgstr "Armar la entrega por EVE-mail"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Sends an in-game mail to the mains behind the owner tags below. Needs a "
"sender character with the <code class=\"text-faint\">esi-mail.send_mail.v1</"
"code> scope."
msgstr ""
"Envía un correo in-game a los mains detrás de las etiquetas de propietario "
"de abajo. Necesita un personaje remitente con el permiso <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">esi-mail.send_mail.v1</code>."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Mail these classifications"
msgstr "Enviar por correo estas clasificaciones"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Targeted mail may carry the sensitive tiers (it is not a broadcast)."
msgstr ""
"El correo dirigido puede incluir los niveles sensibles (no es una difusión)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Sender character id"
msgstr "ID del personaje remitente"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"A corp character that granted the mail-send scope. Leave blank to disable."
msgstr ""
"Un personaje de la corp que haya concedido el permiso de envío de correo. "
"Déjalo en blanco para desactivarlo."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Recipient owner tags"
msgstr "Etiquetas de propietario de los destinatarios"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Space- or comma-separated (e.g. <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">strategic_director</code>). Their mains receive the mail."
msgstr ""
"Separadas por espacios o comas (p. ej. <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">strategic_director</code>). Sus mains reciben el correo."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Command Intelligence · Provider &amp; model · [FORCA] Command Grid"
msgstr "Command Intelligence · Proveedor &amp; modelo · [FORCA] Command Grid"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Provider &amp; model"
msgstr "Proveedor &amp; modelo"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Pick the runtime model name, output sizing, budgets and call discipline. The "
"<span class=\"text-cyan\">API key</span> lives in the environment and is "
"never shown, edited or stored here — only its presence flips the subsystem "
"on."
msgstr ""
"Elige el nombre del modelo de ejecución, el tamaño de salida, los "
"presupuestos y la disciplina de llamadas. La <span class=\"text-cyan\">clave "
"de API</span> vive en el entorno y aquí nunca se muestra, edita ni almacena "
"— solo su presencia activa el subsistema."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Enabled — an <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> is present."
msgstr ""
"Activado — hay una <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> presente."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Disabled — set <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> in the "
"environment to enable Command Intelligence."
msgstr ""
"Desactivado — define <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> en el "
"entorno para activar Command Intelligence."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Model name"
msgstr "Nombre del modelo"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"The runtime model — overrides the env default (e.g. <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">MiniMax-M2.7</code> or <code class=\"text-faint\">MiniMax-M3</code>)."
msgstr ""
"El modelo de ejecución — anula el valor por defecto del entorno (p. ej. "
"<code class=\"text-faint\">MiniMax-M2.7</code> o <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">MiniMax-M3</code>)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Max output tokens"
msgstr "Tokens de salida máximos"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Sized for reasoning plus the answer; raise on a length cut-off. Range 256–"
"65536."
msgstr ""
"Dimensionado para el razonamiento más la respuesta; súbelo si la salida se "
"corta por longitud. Rango 256–65536."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Temperature"
msgstr "Temperatura"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Sampling temperature, 0–1. Lower is more deterministic."
msgstr "Temperatura de muestreo, 0–1. Cuanto más baja, más determinista."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Token budget per report"
msgstr "Presupuesto de tokens por informe"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Hard cap on prompt + completion tokens for a single report."
msgstr "Límite máximo de tokens de prompt + respuesta para un solo informe."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Monthly token ceiling"
msgstr "Techo mensual de tokens"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Safety cap on total tokens spent across all reports in a month."
msgstr ""
"Límite de seguridad sobre el total de tokens gastados en todos los informes "
"de un mes."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Rate limit / hour"
msgstr "Límite de frecuencia / hora"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Reports per hour — backs the breaker counter."
msgstr "Informes por hora — respalda el contador del cortacircuitos."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Repair attempts"
msgstr "Intentos de reparación"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Schema / grounding re-prompts on invalid structured output. Range 0–5."
msgstr ""
"Reintentos de prompt por esquema / grounding cuando la salida estructurada "
"no es válida. Rango 0–5."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Restores the model, budgets and call discipline to the shipped defaults."
msgstr ""
"Restablece el modelo, los presupuestos y la disciplina de llamadas a los "
"valores predeterminados de fábrica."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Role mappings · Comms access · Admin"
msgstr "Asignaciones de roles · Acceso a comms · Admin"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
msgid "← Access sync settings"
msgstr "← Ajustes de sincronización de acceso"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "External comms access"
msgstr "Acceso a comunicaciones externas"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Role mappings"
msgstr "Asignaciones de roles"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid ""
"Each row maps a FORCA entitlement to one platform role/group.\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">This is the managed set</strong> — the sync "
"only ever grants or removes roles listed here;\n"
"  anything else on the server is untouchable. A mapping grants when a pilot "
"has the entitlement; it <em>removes</em>\n"
"  on loss only when its mode is <strong class=\"text-ink\">Authoritative</"
"strong>. New mappings stay in dry-run until you confirm them."
msgstr ""
"Cada fila asigna un derecho de FORCA a un rol/grupo de una plataforma.\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">Este es el conjunto gestionado</strong> — la "
"sincronización solo concede o retira los roles listados aquí;\n"
"  cualquier otra cosa del servidor es intocable. Una asignación concede el "
"rol cuando un piloto tiene el derecho; lo <em>retira</em>\n"
"  al perderlo solo cuando su modo es <strong class=\"text-"
"ink\">Autoritativo</strong>. Las asignaciones nuevas permanecen en "
"simulación hasta que las confirmes."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Add a mapping"
msgstr "Añadir una asignación"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
msgid "Platform"
msgstr "Plataforma"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Entitlement"
msgstr "Derecho"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "e.g. Discord role id"
msgstr "p. ej. ID de rol de Discord"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "e.g. @Member"
msgstr "p. ej. @Member"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Target role id / name"
msgstr "ID / nombre del rol de destino"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Label (optional)"
msgstr "Etiqueta (opcional)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_detail.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_sources.html
msgid "Mode"
msgstr "Modo"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Dry-run"
msgstr "Simulación"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Add mapping"
msgstr "Añadir asignación"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Mappings"
msgstr "Asignaciones"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "authoritative"
msgstr "autoritativo"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "additive"
msgstr "aditivo"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/capsuleer/compare.html
msgid "yes"
msgstr "sí"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/capsuleer/compare.html
msgid "no"
msgstr "no"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Remove this mapping? The sync will stop managing that role."
msgstr ""
"¿Eliminar esta asignación? La sincronización dejará de gestionar ese rol."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "No mappings yet. Until you add one, the sync manages nothing."
msgstr ""
"Aún no hay asignaciones. Hasta que añadas una, la sincronización no gestiona "
"nada."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "Comms access sync"
msgstr "Sincronización de acceso a comms"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Access sync settings"
msgstr "Ajustes de sincronización de acceso"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Linked accounts &amp; ledger"
msgstr "Cuentas vinculadas &amp; registro"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This subsystem drives external-platform roles from corp membership + RBAC.\n"
"  It ships <strong class=\"text-ink\">inert</strong> and is configured "
"entirely here — no server\n"
"  access needed. To go live: <strong class=\"text-ink\">(1)</strong> enter "
"the Discord credentials,\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">(2)</strong> enable the feature, <strong "
"class=\"text-ink\">(3)</strong> arm\n"
"  the platform, and <strong class=\"text-ink\">(4)</strong> take its\n"
"  <a href=\"%(mappings_url)s\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">role "
"mappings</a>\n"
"  out of dry-run. The sync only ever touches roles that appear on the Role "
"mappings page."
msgstr ""
"Este subsistema controla los roles de plataformas externas a partir de la "
"membresía de la corp + RBAC.\n"
"  Se entrega <strong class=\"text-ink\">inerte</strong> y se configura por "
"completo aquí — no hace falta acceso\n"
"  al servidor. Para ponerlo en marcha: <strong class=\"text-ink\">(1)</"
"strong> introduce las credenciales de Discord,\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">(2)</strong> activa la función, <strong "
"class=\"text-ink\">(3)</strong> arma\n"
"  la plataforma y <strong class=\"text-ink\">(4)</strong> saca sus\n"
"  <a href=\"%(mappings_url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">asignaciones de roles</a>\n"
"  de la simulación. La sincronización solo toca los roles que aparecen en la "
"página de Asignaciones de roles."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "Discord credentials"
msgstr "Credenciales de Discord"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid ""
"Create an application at the Discord Developer Portal. Add a bot with the\n"
"    <code>Manage Roles</code> permission and place its role <strong "
"class=\"text-ink\">above</strong> every managed\n"
"    role. Secrets are encrypted at rest and never shown again — leave a "
"secret field blank to keep the current value."
msgstr ""
"Crea una aplicación en el Discord Developer Portal. Añade un bot con el "
