#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_form.html
msgid ""
"Use these to pick values that require real engagement but stay achievable. A "
"safe minimum is roughly half the pro-rated rate; a good booster goal is "
"around the full rate."
msgstr ""
"Úsalos para elegir valores que exijan participación real pero sigan siendo "
"alcanzables. Un mínimo seguro es aproximadamente la mitad de la tasa "
"prorrateada; una buena meta de refuerzo ronda la tasa completa."

