msgstr "Concesión manual · %(name)s · [FORCA] Command Grid"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_grant.html
msgid "Manual grant desk"
msgstr "Mesa de concesiones manuales"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_grant.html
msgid ""
"Reward a pilot with tickets for something the automatic sources can't see — "
"scouting, logi, FC duty. Every grant is audited and appended to the ledger."
msgstr ""
"Recompensa a un piloto con boletos por algo que las fuentes automáticas no "
"pueden ver — scouting, logi, turnos de FC. Cada concesión se audita y se "
"añade al registro."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_grant.html
msgid "← Back to contest"
msgstr "← Volver al concurso"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_grant.html
msgid ""
"Grants only land for <span class=\"text-ink\">enrolled pilots with a valid "
"ESI token</span>. If the character isn't enrolled the server rejects the "
"grant — the pilot must connect their token first. The app never moves ISK; "
"tickets are recorded, prizes delivered by hand."
msgstr ""
"Las concesiones solo se aplican a <span class=\"text-ink\">pilotos inscritos "
"con un token ESI válido</span>. Si el personaje no está inscrito, el "
"servidor rechaza la concesión — el piloto debe conectar su token primero. La "
"app nunca mueve ISK; los boletos se registran y los premios se entregan a "
"mano."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_grant.html
msgid "Amount (tickets)"
msgstr "Cantidad (boletos)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_grant.html
msgid "Shown in the ledger — say what earned the tickets."
msgstr "Se muestra en el registro — indica qué mereció los boletos."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_grant.html
msgid "Internal notes <span class=\"text-faint\">(leaders only)</span>"
msgstr "Notas internas <span class=\"text-faint\">(solo líderes)</span>"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_grant.html
msgid ""
"<span class=\"font-semibold\">Emergency override</span> — grant to a pilot "
"who is not yet enrolled. Director-only, off by default, always audited. Use "
"only when you truly must; the pilot still needs to enrol to win."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"font-semibold\">Anulación de emergencia</span> — conceder a un "
"piloto que aún no está inscrito. Solo para Director, desactivado por "
"defecto, siempre auditado. Úsalo solo cuando sea imprescindible; el piloto "
"igualmente debe inscribirse para poder ganar."

