#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_ineligible.html
msgid ""
"These pilots flew eligible activity during the contest but earned <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">nothing</span> — they aren't enrolled in FORCA, or their "
"ESI token isn't live. Reach out: enrolling and reconnecting is all it takes "
"for them to take part next time."
msgstr ""
"Estos pilotos realizaron actividad elegible durante el concurso pero no "
"ganaron <span class=\"text-ink\">nada</span> — no están inscritos en FORCA o "
"su token ESI no está activo. Contacta con ellos: inscribirse y reconectar es "
"todo lo que hace falta para que participen la próxima vez."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_ineligible.html
msgid ""
"Send a one-time enrolment nudge to each ranked unenrolled pilot with a "
"linked account? Pilots already nudged, opted out, or now enrolled are "
"skipped."
msgstr ""
"¿Enviar un aviso de inscripción único a cada piloto no inscrito de la lista "
"que tenga una cuenta vinculada? Se omiten los pilotos ya avisados, los que "
"se dieron de baja y los que ya están inscritos."

