"Rules whose channels include <span class=\"text-ink\">EVE-mail</span> send "
"in-game from this director to the responsible officer, for <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">high</span>/<span class=\"text-ink\">critical</span> "
"alerts. The chosen director must grant the <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">Readiness mail sender</span> scope on the <a href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" "
"class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">ESI scopes</a> page — until then EVE-"
"mail degrades to a no-op."
msgstr ""
"Las reglas cuyos canales incluyen <span class=\"text-ink\">EVE-mail</span> "
"envían el aviso dentro del juego desde este director al oficial responsable, "
"para alertas <span class=\"text-ink\">altas</span>/<span class=\"text-"
"ink\">críticas</span>. El director elegido debe conceder el scope <span "
"class=\"font-mono\">Readiness mail sender</span> en la página de <a "
"href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">scopes de ESI</"
"a>; hasta entonces EVE-mail queda sin efecto."

