#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/doctrines.html
msgid "Readiness · Doctrine classification"
msgstr "Preparación · Clasificación de doctrine"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/doctrines.html
msgid ""
"Mark which doctrines are <span class=\"text-ink\">primary</span>, <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">mandatory</span> or <span class=\"text-ink\">alliance</"
"span>, set a retirement date, and a minimum pilot count. A <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">mandatory</span> doctrine that's under-crewed raises a "
"high-severity finding; a doctrine past its <span class=\"text-"
"cyan\">retirement date</span> raises a replace-it finding. Leaving a "
"doctrine unclassified has no effect on the index."
msgstr ""
"Marca qué doctrines son <span class=\"text-ink\">primary</span>, <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">mandatory</span> o <span class=\"text-ink\">alliance</"
"span>, fija una fecha de retirada y un número mínimo de pilotos. Una "
"doctrine <span class=\"text-cyan\">mandatory</span> sin pilotos suficientes "
"genera un hallazgo de gravedad alta; una doctrine que ha superado su <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">fecha de retirada</span> genera un hallazgo de "
"reemplazo. Dejar una doctrine sin clasificar no afecta al índice."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/doctrines.html
msgid "Primary"
msgstr "Primary"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/doctrines.html
