#: templates/planetary/_onboarding.html
msgid "Passive ISK from the ground up"
msgstr "ISK pasivo desde cero"

#: templates/planetary/_onboarding.html
msgid ""
"You deploy colonies on planets. <span class=\"text-ink\">Extractor</span> "
"planets pull\n"
"    raw resources and refine them; <span class=\"text-ink\">factory</span> "
"planets combine\n"
"    materials into higher-value goods. Reset the extractors on your own "
"schedule, haul the\n"
"    output to market, and it earns while you're doing other things. Taxes, "
"hauling and\n"
"    market prices decide whether it's worth it — this planner does that "
"maths for you."
msgstr ""
"Despliegas colonias en planetas. Los planetas <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">extractores</span> extraen\n"
"    recursos en bruto y los refinan; los planetas <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">de fábrica</span> combinan\n"
"    materiales en bienes de mayor valor. Reinicia los extractores según tu "
"propio horario, transporta la\n"
"    producción al mercado y genera ingresos mientras haces otras cosas. Los "
"impuestos, el transporte y los\n"
"    precios de mercado deciden si vale la pena: este planificador hace esos "
"cálculos por ti."

#: templates/planetary/_onboarding.html
msgid "The eight planet types"
msgstr "Los ocho tipos de planeta"

